com.mesosphere.sdk.specification

Interface PodInstance

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPodInstance

    public interface PodInstance
    A PodInstance defines a particular instance of a PodSpec. PodSpecs have an associated count, see (PodSpec.getCount()). When expanding that PodSpec to match the required count, PodInstances are generated.
